Name: Hampton Roads Bankshares, Inc
Description: Hampton Roads Bankshares, Inc. is a United States-based bank holding company. The Company is a banking and financial services organization. Its subsidiaries include Bank of Hampton Roads, Shore Bank and Gateway Bank & Trust Co. It provides the financial services that help people to run business. Its services include Business Checking Accounts, Business Savings Accounts, Business Loans and Online Services. the Company also provides personal banking, such as Personal Checking Accounts, Personal Savings Accounts, Personal Credit Services and Online Services.
